  "Description": {
    "English": "Partial coordinate data, acquired from a troubled <span class=\"name name-stellar\">freighter captain</span>. The chart is signed with a snippet of pirate manifesto:<br><br>\"We Blight this new galaxy, as we did the last, as we will the next!\"<br><br>The data is of value to pirate faction <span class=\"name name-special\">The Blight</span>, who attempted to retrieve it by violent means.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "部分坐标数据，从一个备受困扰的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">货船船长</span>处获得。图表上书写着一句海盗宣言：<br><br>“我们给新星系带来瘟疫，一如之前所为，亦如今后将为！”<br><br>这些数据对海盗派系<span class=\"name name-special\">瘟疫</span>来说非常有价值，他们试图通过暴力手段夺回这些数据。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "部分座標資料，從不堪海盜騷擾的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">貨船船長</span>身上取得。該圖表上簽署了一段海盜宣言：<br><br>「我們會毀滅這個新銀河系，就像我們毀滅上一個一樣，我們也會毀滅下一個！」<br><br>這份資料對海盜陣營<span class=\"name name-special\">「毀滅」</span>很有價值，他們曾試圖用暴力手段取回。"
  },
